general.name: photoWISE
general.short: migrated from old datamodel - needs update
general.description:
Contains cross-matches between the SDSS photoObj objects and the WISE All-Sky Release catalog. Please refer to the WISE catalog explanatory supplement for full details on the WISE catalog columns. These files only include a subset of the columns.
The astrometric matching uses a 4 arcsecond radius. The matching is many-to-many: SDSS objects may appear multiple times and WISE objects may appear multiple times.
general.naming_convention: photoWISE-[0-9]{6}-[1-6].fits; photoWISE-RRRRRR-C.fits for run RRRRRR and camcol C.

changelog.description: Describes changes to the datamodel product and/or file structure from one release to another
